						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up on the roadside near the Taluk office.</p>						

						<p>This is dated cyclic year <hi rend="bold"><hi rend="italic">Prajōtpatti, Kārttīka ba. 1.</hi></hi></p>						

						<p>It records an endowment made for the worship of a deity installed in a Jaṅgamma <hi rend="italic">maṭha</hi> by one Pavāḍada Chikka Vāmppayya and also states that the gift was given to Guṉdi Yellappa. In late characters.</p>						

						</summary>
